# Crystal Cave Skip (CCS)

This skip is allow the player to the the major part of the [crystal cave](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/crystal-cave) leading to [Seath](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/seath-the-scaleless). It is very precise and require a lot of practice for the glitched version.

## External Ressources

### Glitchless Method

The glitchless method is not as fast as the classic CCS but saves around 10sec compared to a classic pathing.

Glitchless CCS : [https://youtu.be/mVoS9mI0pYM?t=1773](https://youtu.be/mVoS9mI0pYM?t=1773) by m3dic on YouTube.

### Classic Method (Glitched)

This skip saves around 25sec compared to a classic pathing and 14sec compared to the glitchless method. Recently some players discovered that the slope qui-out method was easier in mid roll tier.

### Ressources

Slope Quit-out CCS : [https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0?t=1490](https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0?t=1490) by aeiou on YouTube.

Memeroll CCS (very precise and not recommended): [https://youtu.be/Odjz7l62hYQ](https://youtu.be/Odjz7l62hYQ) by San on YouTube.
